---
source: crates/test-framework/src/snapshot/mod.rs
description: "Query: clickbench_q25"
---
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                            |
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: hits.SearchPhrase                                                                                                                   |
|               |   Sort: to_timestamp(hits.EventTime) ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=10                                                                                   |
|               |     Projection: hits.SearchPhrase, hits.EventTime                                                                                               |
|               |       Filter: hits.SearchPhrase != LargeUtf8("")                                                                                                |
|               |         TableScan: hits projection=[EventTime, SearchPhrase]                                                                                    |
| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[SearchPhrase@0 as SearchPhrase]                                                                                           |
|               |   SortPreservingMergeExec: [to_timestamp(EventTime@1) ASC NULLS LAST], fetch=10                                                                 |
|               |     SortExec: TopK(fetch=10), expr=[to_timestamp(EventTime@1) ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                     |
|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[SearchPhrase@1 as SearchPhrase, EventTime@0 as EventTime]                                                           |
|               |         CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                             |
|               |           FilterExec: SearchPhrase@1 !=                                                                                                         |
|               |             SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                  |
|               |               BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                |
|               |                 DataSourceExec: partitions=16, partition_sizes=[382, 382, 382, 382, 382, 382, 382, 382, 381, 381, 381, 381, 381, 381, 381, 386] |
|               |                                                                                                                                                 |
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
